snippet.title: Puyo Puyo Champions - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Go head-to-head against your friends or against the world in Puyo Puyo Champions, out now on Nintendo Switch for only $9.99! Featuring a new 8-player local tournament mode, a Battle History feature showcasing the biggest moments of a match, and the option between English or Japanese voices, there's no better time to experience all the fun-filled, fast-paced, action-packed thrills this series has to offer!

Learn more about Puyo Puyo Champions! https://bit.ly/2Y0Ulw0

#NintendoSwitch #PuyoPuyo
